title: ARCTIC ARMAGEDDON | Action Disaster Thriller | Free Full Movie
description:
After an earthquake hits in the middle of the Atlantic, the warm water currents flowing to the Arctic stop, causing the global temperature to plunge. As the world freezes over and cities fall to ruin, scientists must figure out how to get the water flowing again before the world descends into the next ice age.

Directed by: James Mahoney
Starring: Patrick Labyorteaux, Joe Finfera, Lindsey Marie Wilson
